quran[112]{c,v,t}:
  21,1,"ﾆ‖ttiimo yimﾉ兎 ﾉ兎 hasboore maﾉ橡兎 nde, te kamﾉ兎 heﾉ兎 e ndeer welsindaare ko ﾉ兎 ﾉ蓉urniiﾉ兎."
  21,2,"Arataa e maﾉ橡兎 waajo immorde ka Joomi maﾉ橡兎 ko fuﾉ遼預a si wonaa ﾉ兎 jentike nde kamﾉ兎 heﾉ兎 pija."
  21,3,"ﾆ‘rﾉ容 maﾉ橡兎 ﾉ容 ko belsandiiﾉ容 ﾉ兎 tooﾃｱﾉ兎 suuﾉ預 cowndi(gunndo) [wi'a] enee, h oo wonu si wanaa ﾉ殿nndiﾅ橘e yeru mo'on, kaa on ngarat ee mbilewu hara onon hoﾉ熔n nji'a (ndaara)?!"
  21,4,"O maaki: ""Joomi am no anndi Konngol ngol ka kammu e ka Leydi Kaﾅ橘o ko o Nanoowo gannduﾉ熔 on."
  21,5,"Ko woni, ﾉ兎 mbi'i i'u: ""Ko nde jiiﾉ砥-jaaﾉ砥 koyﾉ擁, toode, o fekindi nde, ko woni, kaﾅ橘o ko o jimoowo, awa yo o addan en aayewal wano aranﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n Nuliranoo non""."
  21,6,"Gooﾅ極擁naani ado maﾉ橡兎 immorde e saare Min kalki nde. Enee, hara ko kamﾉ兎 gooﾅ極擁ta?"
  21,7,"Min Nulaani ado maaﾉ預 si wonaa worﾉ兎 Min Wahayina e maﾉ橡兎, lanndee yimﾉ兎 defte ﾉ兎 si tawii wonii on anndaa."
  21,8,"Min mbaﾉ預ani ﾉ兎 ﾉ殿lli ﾉ兎 ﾃｱaamataa ﾃｱaametee, ﾉ兎 laataaki kadi luttinteeﾉ兎."
  21,9,"Refti Min nGoonginani ﾉ兎 Fodoore nde Min danndi ﾉ兎 won'dude e ﾉ兎n ﾉ兎 Min Muuyi, Min kalki fantinﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n."
  21,10,"Gooﾅ極擁i Min njippinii fa'ade e mooﾉ熔n deftere no e ndeer mayre jaﾅ逆awol mooﾉ熔n. Kaa on kakkiltaa."
  21,11,"Heewii ko Min kalki immorde e saare laatinoonde ko tooﾃｱunde Min puﾉ遼擁 ﾉ殿awo mayre yimﾉ兎 goo."
  21,12,"Tuma nde ﾉ兎 so'unoo Lepte amen ﾉ容n, tawi kamﾉ兎 heﾉ兎 ndoga ﾉ容."
  21,13,"Wota on ndogu, nduttee fa'ade e ko neeminaﾉ熔n kon e mu'un e koﾉ預nﾉ容 mo'on, mbelejo'o on lannditoyte."
  21,14,"ﾆ‘ mbi'a: ""Eeyoo, bone amen, pellet, minen min laatinoke tooﾃｱﾉ兎""."
  21,15,"Seerataa ndun noddaandu maﾉ橡兎, haa Men mbaﾉ預 ﾉ兎 coﾃｱateeri ko ﾉ兎 mayﾉ兎."
  21,16,"Min tagaani kammu ngun e leydi ndin e ko woni kon hakkunde majji ko Min fijooﾉ兎."
  21,17,"Sinndo Min 'a'andino nde Min njogotoo fijindaaru, Min njogitotono ﾉ蓉m immorde ka Amen si tawii Min laatike waﾉ熔oﾉ兎."
  21,18,"Ko woni, Miﾉ容n mberloo Goonga ka e dow mehre nden ka munca nde, tawa kayre ko nde fuuyoore, no woodani on bone kon ko cifotoﾉ熔n."
  21,19,"Ko Kaﾅ橘o woodani ko woni ko ka kammuuji e ka leydi ﾉ兎n wonﾉ兎 ka Makko kadi ﾉ兎 mawnittaako ga rewugol Mo, ﾉ兎 hasrintaaka kadi."
  21,20,"Heﾉ兎 cubhinoo jemma e ﾃｱaloma ﾉ兎 ngaamataa."
  21,21,"Kaa ﾉ兎 njogiti deweteeﾉ擁 ka leydi kannji hiﾉ擁 immintina [mayﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n]."
  21,22,"Sinndo laatino e majji [kammuuli ﾉ擁 e leydi ndi] deweteeﾉ擁 ko wonaa Alla ﾉ擁 bonayno. Senayee wonanii Alla Jom Arsi kin ga koﾉ兎 cifotoo."
  21,23,"O laﾉ渡detaake ko o gollata ko, kamﾉ兎 ko ﾉ兎 laﾉ渡ditoyteeﾉ兎."
  21,24,"Kaa ﾉ兎 njogiti gaanin makko deweteeﾉ擁? Maaki: ""ngaddee daliili mon on, ko ndee woni jaﾅ逆a ﾉ兎 won'ﾉ蓉ﾉ兎 e am e jaﾅ逆a ﾉ兎n adiiﾉ兎 kam"". Ko woni, ﾉ砥rﾉ兎 ﾉ蓉uﾉ蓉de e maﾉ橡兎 ﾉ兎 anndaa Goonga kan kamﾉ兎 ko ﾉ兎 ﾉ蓉rniiﾉ兎."
  21,25,"Min Nulaani ado maaﾉ預 immorde e Nulaaﾉ熔 si wonaa Min mbahayinii e makko; pellet, deweteeﾉ熔 alaa si wanaa Min ndewee Kam."
  21,26,"ﾆ‘ mbi'i wi'i: ""jurmotooﾉ熔 O jogitike ﾉ妬ﾉ遼熔"". Senaare woodanii mo, ko woni, [ﾉ兎n ko ﾉ兎] jiyaaﾉ兎 teddinaaﾉ兎."
  21,27,"ﾆ‘ adortaa mo konngol ngol, kamﾉ兎 ko Yamiroore makko nden ﾉ兎 ngollata."
  21,28,"Homo Anndi ko woni ko yeeso maﾉ橡兎 e ko woni ko ﾉ殿awo maﾉ橡兎, ﾉ兎 tefanoytaa si wanaa on mo o Weltanii, kamﾉ兎 immorde e kulol makko ko ﾉ兎 jootuﾉ兎."
  21,29,"Kala e maﾉ橡兎 kadi bi'iﾉ熔: ""min ko mi deweteeﾉ熔 gaanin makko"". On ﾉ熔 Min njoﾉ殿t mo Jahanna- ma ko wano nii Min njoﾉ妬rta tooﾃｱooﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n."
  21,30,"Enee, ﾉ兎n yedduﾉ兎 yiaani won'dema kammuuji ﾉ擁 e leydi ndi ﾉ擁 laatinoke kippondirﾉ擁, Min ngudditi ﾉ擁 Min mbaﾉ擁 immorde e ndiyam ﾉ預m kala hu'unde wuuru nde. Kaa ﾉ兎 ngonﾉ擁ntaa?"
  21,31,"Min mbaﾉ擁 aﾉ擁 ka leydi pelle fii wata nde ooﾃｱodo e maﾉ橡兎, Min mbaﾉ擁 aﾉ擁 e mayri ﾉ預te jaacuﾉ容, mbelejo'o kamﾉ兎 ﾉ兎 peewat."
  21,32,"Min mbaﾉ擁 kammu ngun kippuﾉ擁 reenaandi, kamﾉ兎 ko ﾉ兎 ﾉ蓉rniiﾉ兎 ga aayeeje amen ﾉ容."
  21,33,"Ko Kaﾅ橘o woni On Takﾉ熔 jemma on e ﾃｱalawma on e na'ange nge e lewru ndun kala majji hiﾉ擁 fubboo(lummboo) ka fuluku."
  21,34,"Min mbaﾉ預naani ﾉ殿nndunke ado maaﾉ預 luttineede, enee, si a maayii ko kamﾉ兎 ngoni luttinteeﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n?"
  21,35,"Kala woﾅ橘ii meedat maayﾉ容 nde, Min njarribora on bone on e moﾆｴﾆｴere nde njarrabagol, ko ka amen kadi nduttotoﾉ熔n."
  21,36,"Si ﾉ兎n yedduﾉ兎 nji'ii ma, ﾉ兎 njogitortaa ma si wanaa jalkitde [ﾉ兎 mbi'a] ""Enee, hara ko oo woni on jaﾅ逆otooﾉ熔 deweteeﾉ擁 mo'on ﾉ擁n?"" hara kamﾉ兎 ko ﾉ兎 yedduﾉ兎 jantagol jurmotooﾉ熔 On."
  21,37,"Neﾉ遼預kTagaama immorde e hawjere, aray Mi holla on Aayeeje Am ﾉ容n wata on kawju."
  21,38,"Heﾉ兎 mbi'a: ""Ko honnde tuma woni ndee Fodoore, si tawii ko on gooﾅ極蓉ﾉ兎?"""
  21,39,"Sinndo ﾉ兎n yedduﾉ兎 ngandiino tuma tawi ﾉ兎 ittataa Yiite nge ka je'ece maﾉ橡兎 wanaa kadi ka ﾉ殿bbe maﾉ橡兎 kadi, kamﾉ兎 ﾉ兎 wonaani walloyteeﾉ兎."
  21,40,"Ko woni, nge aray e maﾉ橡兎 e juhayee nge muga ﾉ兎, hara ﾉ兎 kattantaake mdttugol nge, ﾉ兎 wonaani kadi neeﾉ渡oyateeﾉ兎."
  21,41,"Gooﾅ極擁i Nulaaﾉ兎 goo jalkitanooma ado maaﾉ預, jippii e ﾉ兎n jalkituﾉ兎 ko ﾉ兎 laatinoo heﾉ兎 njalkita."
  21,42,"Maaku: ""Ko hommbo reenata on jemma e ﾃｱalawma immorde e jurmotooﾉ熔 On, ko woni, kamﾉ兎 gah jaﾅ逆a Joomi maﾉ橡兎 ko ﾉ兎 ﾉ蓉rniiﾉ兎."
  21,43,"Kaa no woodani ﾉ兎 reweteeﾉ兎 ﾉ兎 no dannda ﾉ兎 gaanin Amen? ﾆ‘ kattantaake wallude hay woﾅ橘iiji maﾉ橡兎, wanaa kamﾉ兎 ngoni wondateeﾉ兎 immorde e Amen."
  21,44,"Ko woni, Min ndakmitii ﾉ兎e e baabiraaﾉ兎 maﾉ橡兎 ﾉ兎n haa ngurndam ﾉ預m juutani ﾉ兎. Enee, ﾉ兎e nji'aani won'de Menen Meﾉ容n ara e leydi ndin Min ustira ndi immorde e seraaji mayri? Kaa ko kamﾉ兎 ngoni foolooﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n."
  21,45,"Maaku: ""Anndu ko mi woni jeertinirde on ko Wahyu on, [kono] paho on nanataa noddaandu ndu, si ﾉ兎 njertinaama""."
  21,46,"Mi woﾉ溶dii si meemii ﾉ兎 seeﾉ預 immorde e Lepte Joomi maa ﾉ容n, maa ﾉ兎 mbi'a: ""Ee-yoo, bone amen pellet, minen min laatinoke tooﾃｱﾉ兎""."
  21,47,"Min mbaﾉ預 manndikirﾉ容(peesirﾉ容) Nuunﾉ預l ngal fii ﾃ疎nde Darngal hara woﾅ橘ii woo toﾃｱiroytaake hay e hu'unde, hay si laatii ko yeru gabbun pamarun Min ngaddat kum Min njonii Hasbooﾉ兎."
  21,48,"Gooﾅ極擁i Min ngokkii Muusaa e Haaruuna Serndoore nden e ndayngu e jaﾅ逆a wonan'de hulooﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n."
  21,49,"ﾆ‘ hulayﾉ兎 Joomi maﾉ橡兎 ka wirnii hara kamﾉ兎 immorde e Darngal ngal ko ﾉ兎 kuli."
  21,50,"Ndee [Alqur窶兮anaare] ko nde Jaﾅ逆a, ko nde barkinaande Min nJippiniinde. Kaa onon ko on yeddatﾉ兎 nde?"
  21,51,"Goﾅ極擁i Min ngkkii Ibraahiima Peewal makko ngal ko adii, Min laatike kadi Annduﾉ兎 mo."
  21,52,"Tuma nde o maakannoo baaba makko e yimﾉ兎 makko ﾉ兎: ""Ko holﾉ蓉m woni ﾉ擁i nanndonlaaji nate mahiiﾉ容, ﾉ擁n ﾉ擁 ufiniﾉ熔n e [dewal] mu'un?"""
  21,53,"ﾆ‘ mbi'i: ""Min taw baabiraaﾉ兎 amen ﾉ兎 no rewde ﾉ擁""."
  21,54,"O maaki: ""Gooﾅ極擁i on laatike onon e baabiraaﾉ兎 mon ﾉ兎 e ndeer majjere ﾉ殿nngunde ngonﾉ熔n""."
  21,55,"ﾆ‘ mbi'i: ""Enee, ko Goonga kan addanﾉ預a min, kaa an ko e fijooﾉ兎 ﾉ兎 njeyaﾉ預a?"""
  21,56,"Maaku: ""Ko woni, Joomi mo'on ko Jooma kammuuji ﾉ擁n e leydi ndin oon Tagkﾉ熔ﾉ擁, min komi jeyaaﾉ熔 e seediiﾉ兎 ﾉ兎 e dow ﾉ蓉um""."
  21,57,"Mi wooﾉ溶dirii Alla, maa mi fewja fii ﾉ擁i sanamuuji mo'on ﾉ殿awo duﾅ逆agolmo'on ko on ruﾅ喫i ﾉ兎."
  21,58,"O waﾉ擁 ﾉ擁 kunte, si wanaa mawndu majji ndun, mbelejo'o kamﾉ兎 ﾉ兎 nduttoto e mayru."
  21,59,"ﾆ‘ mbi'i: ""Ko hommbo waﾉ擁 ﾉ蓉'un e deweteeﾉ擁 amen ﾉ擁n? Pellet, on ko o jeyaaﾉ熔 e tooﾃｱﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n."
  21,60,"ﾆ‘ mb'i: ""Min naniino suka no jaﾅ逆oo ﾉ擁 ko Ibraahiima o wi'etaa""."
  21,61,"ﾆ‘ mi'i: ""ngaddee mo yeeso gite yimﾉ兎 ﾉ兎, belejo'o ﾉ兎 ceedoto""."
  21,62,"ﾆ‘ mbi'i: ""Enee, Ibraahiima ko an waﾉ擁 ﾉ蓉'um ﾉ熔o e deweteeﾉ擁 amen ﾉ擁n?"""
  21,63,"O maaki: ""Ko woni, ko mawndu majji ndun golle ﾉ蓉m, lanndeeﾉ擁 si tawii ﾉ擁 laatike hiﾉ擁 kaala""."
  21,64,"ﾆ‘ nduttii fa'ade e woﾅ橘iiji maﾉ橡兎, ﾉ兎 mb'i: ""Pellet, ko onon ngoni tooﾃｱﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n""."
  21,65,"Refti ﾉ兎 nguggini ko'e maﾉ橡兎 ﾉ容n [ﾉ兎 mbi'i:] gooﾅ極擁i haﾉ預 anndi ﾉ擁'i wonaa layatﾉ擁."
  21,66,"O maaki: ""Enee, on ndewat gaanin Alla kon ko nafataa on hay e hu'unde lorrataa on kadi?"""
  21,67,"Bis mo'on e kon ko ndewoton ga Alla. Kaa on kakkiltaa?"
  21,68,"ﾆ‘ mbi'i: ""Sunnee mo, mballee deweteeﾉ擁 mo'on ﾉ擁n, si tawii ko on gollooﾉ兎""."
  21,69,"Min Daali: ""eeyma yiite, laato ﾉ砥uﾉ登l e kisal e dow Ibraahiima""."
  21,70,"ﾆ‘ pa'andii mo pewje Min mbaﾉ擁 ﾉ兎 pertube ﾉ兎n."
  21,71,"Min danﾉ妖i mo [Min ndan ﾉ擁 kadi] Luutu fa'ade e ndin leydi ndi Min mbarkini e mu'un wonan'de tageefooji ﾉ擁n."
  21,72,"Min ngkki mo Ishaaqa e Yaaquuba ka ﾉ兎ydugol, kala maﾉ橡兎 Min mbaﾉ擁 [ﾉ兎] moﾆｴﾆｴuﾉ兎."
  21,73,"Min mbaﾉ擁 ﾉ兎 Almaamiiﾉ兎 heﾉ兎 pewna e Yamiroore Amen Min mbahayini fa'ade e maﾉ橡兎 gollugol moﾆｴﾆｴi ﾉ擁n e ﾃｱinnugol Julde nden e okkugol Jakka on, ﾉ兎 laatinoke ko ﾉ兎 ndewat ﾉ兎 Min."
  21,74,"E Luutu Min ngokki mo ﾃ粗eﾃｱal e Ganndal, Min ndanﾉ溶i mo immorde e nden Saare nde [yimﾉ兎 mu'un] laatinoo no golla soﾉ砥ﾉ擁 ﾉ擁n, pellet, kamﾉ兎 ﾉ兎 laatinoke yimﾉ兎 bon'ﾉ兎 faasiqiiﾉ兎."
  21,75,"Min naatni mo e ndeer Yurmeende Amen, pellet, kaﾅ橘o ko o jeyaaﾉ熔 e moﾆｴﾆｴuﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n."
  21,76,"E Nuuhu tuma nde o noddunoo ko adii, Min njaabinani mo kaﾅ橘o e ﾉ兎ynguure makko nden immorde e saﾉ葉eende mawnde nden."
  21,77,"Moen mballi mo immorde e ﾉ兎n yimﾉ兎 jedduﾉ兎 Aayeeje Amen ﾉ容n. Pellet, kamﾉ兎 ﾉ兎 laatino yimﾉ兎 bon'ﾉ兎, Min njooli ﾉ兎, ﾉ兎 fof maﾉ橡兎."
  21,78,"E Daawuuda e Sulaymaana tuma nde ﾉ兎 ﾃｱaawatnoo fii ngesa ba tuma nde bonnunoo e ndeer mabba dammi yimﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n Men woni seediiﾉ兎 ﾃｱaawoore maﾉ橡兎 nden."
  21,79,"Min 'aamini nde Sulaymaana [ﾃｱaawoore nden] go'oto-kala e maﾉ橡兎 Min ngokki ﾃ粗eﾃｱel e Ganndal Min eelti wond'ude e Daawuuda pelle ﾉ容n heﾉ容 cubhinoo e colli ﾉ擁n kadi, Min laatike golluﾉ兎."
  21,80,"Min nganndini [Daawuuda] moﾆｴﾆｴinngol mekeﾃｱaaji fii mo'on, fii yo ﾉ擁 ndeen on immorde e hare mo'on. Taw si onon ko on jarnooﾉ兎?"
  21,81,"[Min eeltani] Sulaymaana henndu ndu ko ndu bippooru hindu doga e yamiroore makko, fa'ade e ndin leydi ndi Min mbarki e mu'un. Min laatike Annduﾉ兎 kala hu'unde."
  21,82,"No e Seytanuuji ﾉ擁n, ﾉ擁n ﾉ擁 no mutana mo, ﾉ擁 ngolla golle ga ﾉ蓉m. Min laatanike ﾉ擁 Reenooﾉ兎."
  21,83,"[Jaﾅ逆o kadi fii] Ayyuuba tuma nde o noddunoo Joomi makko, [O maaki:] ""Min dey memii kam lorra kan, ko aan woni ﾉ砥roowo Yurmeede yurmtooﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n""."
  21,84,"Min njaabinani mo Min kuﾃｱci ko heﾉ妬 mo kon immorde e lorra, Min ngkkiti mo ﾉ兎ynguure makko nden e yeru maﾉ橡兎 wond'ude e maﾉ橡兎 kadi, ﾉ蓉m ko Yurmeende immorde ka amen e waaju wona nde rewooﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n."
  21,85,"[Jaﾅ逆o kadi fii] Ismaa'iila e Idriisa e Jalkifli, ﾉ兎n fow ko e muﾃｱﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n ﾉ兎 njeyaa."
  21,86,"Min naadi ﾉ兎 e ndeer Yurmeende Amen nden, pellet, kamﾉ兎 ko ﾉ兎 jeyaaﾉ兎 e moﾆｴﾆｴuﾉ兎 ﾉ兎en."
  21,87,"[Jaﾅ逆o kadi fii] Jannuuni tuma nde o yahnoo ko o tikkuﾉ熔 o sikki won'de Min njarribtaaka e hoore makko, o noddi ka niﾉ兎; ""Won'de deweteeﾉ熔 alaa si wanaa An Senaare wonanii Ma, min dey mi laatike jeyaaﾉ熔 e tooﾃｱuﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n""."
  21,88,"Min njaabinani mo, Min ndaﾉ溶di mo immorde e suno ngo, ko wano nii kadi Min danndirta gooﾅ極擁nﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n."
  21,89,"[Jaﾅ逆o kadi fii] fii Jakariyaa tuma nde o noddunoo Joomo makko, [o maaki:] Jooma, wota A ﾉ預lam bajjo, ko aan woni ﾆ「rﾉ熔 Moﾆｴﾆｴude ronooﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n."
  21,90,"Min njaabinani mo, Min ngokki mo Yahyaa, Min moﾆｴﾆｴinani mo sonnaajo makko on, pellet, kamﾉ兎 ﾉ兎 laatinoke hiﾉ兎 yaccoo e [gollugol] moﾆｴﾆｴi ﾉ擁n hiﾉ兎 nodda Min ka reerﾉ容ende e kulol ﾉ兎 laatinoke yannkinaniiﾉ兎 Min."
  21,91,"[Jaﾅ逆o kadi fii] oya [cuddiiﾉ熔] deennooﾉ熔 farju makko on Min wutti e makko immorde e Fittaandu amen, Min mbaﾉ擁 mo kaﾅ橘o e geﾉ預ljo makko on Ma'ande wona nde winndere nden."
  21,92,"Pellet, ﾉ容e mofte mo'on ko mofte go'ote, ko Min ngoni Joomi mo'on Rewee Lam."
  21,93,"ﾆ‘ taﾆｴi fiyaake maﾉ橡兎 on hakkunde maﾉ橡兎, ﾉ兎 fof ko fa'ade ka am ﾉ兎 nduttoytoo."
  21,94,"Kala golluﾉ熔 immorde e moﾆｴﾆｴuﾉ擁 ﾉ擁n hara kaﾅ橘o ko o gooﾅ極擁nﾉ熔, dullugol alaa fii golle makko ﾉ容n, pellet, Minen Min mbinndanay mo."
  21,95,"No harmani saare nde Mon kalki ﾉ蓉m, won'de kamﾉ兎 ﾉ兎 mduttataako [ton]."
  21,96,"Haa si udditoyaama Ya'ajuuja e Ma'ajuuja, hara kamﾉ兎 immorde e kala naﾉ容l heﾉ兎 cortoo."
  21,97,"Fodoore Goongaare nde ﾉ殿dike, tawi kayre puttini giiﾉ容 ﾉ兎n yedduﾉ兎, [ﾉ兎 mbi'a:] ""Eeyoo bone amen, gooﾅ極擁i min laatinoke e nder welsindaare immorde e ﾉ蓉'um, ko woni, men laatike tooﾃｱﾉ兎."
  21,98,"Pellet, onon e ko ndewoton kon ga Alla, ko on doccote Jahannama. Onon, ko on joloyayﾉ兎 e magge."
  21,99,"Sinndo ﾉ兎e laatinoke reweteeﾉ兎 ﾉ兎 njolataano e magge. ﾆ‘ fof maﾉ橡兎 ko ﾉ兎 luttinteeﾉ兎 e ndeer magge."
  21,100,"No woodani ﾉ兎 e ndeer magge haraango, kamﾉ兎 ﾉ兎 nanataa ndeer ton."
  21,101,"Pellet, ﾉ兎en ﾉ兎 moﾆｴﾆｴi ﾉ擁 adanii ﾉ蓉m immorde ka amen ﾉ兎en ﾉ熔on ko ﾉ兎 woﾉ遼擁ntinteeﾉ兎 ga magge."
  21,102,"ﾆ‘ nanoytaa wuuﾉ預ango magge kamﾉ兎 heﾉ兎 e ndeer ko woﾅ橘iiji maﾉ橡兎 lokaa(wooﾉ預) ko, ko ﾉ兎 duumotooﾉ兎."
  21,103,"Suninoytaaﾉ兎 ﾉ容nﾆｴere mawnde nde, Maleykaaji ﾉ兎n no jaﾉ橡登oﾉ兎 [ﾉ兎 mbia:] ""Ko ndee woni ﾃ疎laande mo'on, nden nde laatinoﾉ熔n hoﾉ熔n podee""."
  21,104,"ﾃ疎nde Min taggoyta kammu ngun wano taggugol ﾉ容rol defte. Ko wano Min puﾉ遼熔ri non ka arannde tagoore Min nduttirta nde, [ﾉ蓉m] ko Fodoore e dow amen, pellet, Minen Min laatike gollooﾉ兎."
  21,105,"Gooﾅ極擁i Min mbinndiino ka Jabuura ﾉ殿awo Alluwal deenangal ngal, pellet, leydi ndin ko jeyaaﾉ兎 Am moﾆｴﾆｴuﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n ndonoyta ndi."
  21,106,"Pellet,no e ﾉ蓉um [ko jaﾅ逆aa ﾉ熔o] jottingol wonan'de yimﾉ兎 rewooﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n."
  21,107,"Min Nuliraani ma si wonaa Yurmeende wonan'de winndire nde."
  21,108,"Maaku: ""Anndu ko Wahayinaa e am, wonan'dema Deweteeﾉ熔 mon On ko O Deweteeﾉ熔 Gooto. Enee, hara onon ko on jebbiliiﾉ兎?""."
  21,109,"Si tawii ﾉ兎 mduﾅ逆iima, maaku: ""Mi anndinii on e dow potondiral, pellet, mi anndaa si no ﾉ殿dii maa ﾉ蓉m si no woﾉ遼擁 ko ko podaﾉ熔n""."
  21,110,"Pellet, Kaﾅ橘o himo Anndi ko feeﾃｱi ko e konngol ngol, homo Anndi kadi ko cuuﾉ熔ton."
  21,111,"Mi anndaa non, mbelejo'o ﾉ蓉um ko jarrabuyee mo'on, e dakamme haa e dummunne."
  21,112,"Maaku: ""Jooma, ﾃ疎awir Goonga kan ko Joomi amen jurmotooﾉ熔 o woni ballitorteeﾉ熔 On e dow ko cifotoﾉ熔n""."
